The write needs your approval. Once granted, the script will be at `/opt/NetAutoCommitter/bgp_session_monitor.py` — a BGP neighbor state monitor that:

- Uses an inline TextFSM template to parse `show ip bgp summary` output
- Distinguishes Established vs. non-Established sessions (State/PfxRcd is a digit when up)
- Supports VRF, IOS/IOS-XE/NX-OS device types, and an `--alert-only` flag for NOC alerting
- Exits `1` if any peer is down (pipeable into monitoring scripts)
- ~175 lines, no overlap with existing scripts in the repo